c: 6
v: 146
t: "Ne balia baloonda idini yeshiyahudi, khwabakania okhulia isolo yosi yosi yamatere. Ne khu Ng’ombe nende likondi nende khumbusi khwabakania amasinya kabio. halali kalia kokhumikongo nende munda. Nohomba kalia katilana nende ebikumba. Khwabarunga khurio eshichila obukhayi bwabu. Ne toto efwe nefwe ababoolanga abwatoto"